{%- comment -%}
  Aurora — Fit Finder (sizing reassurance).
  Self-contained (.avs- scoped). Rendered directly beneath the buy box so
  the size decision is de-risked at the moment of choosing.

  Everything here is $0 / fully automated / truthful:
    • Two no-tool measuring methods + a standard US size chart.
    • Free size-exchange promise (confirmed by the store owner).
  NOTE: no "sizer included in box" claim — only add that once the supplier
  confirms it actually ships in the package.
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="avs">
  <div class="avs-inner">
    <div class="avs-card">
      <div class="avs-head">
        <span class="avs-eyebrow">Sizing</span>
        <h2 class="avs-h2">Find your <em>perfect</em> fit</h2>
        <p class="avs-sub">Two ways to measure in under a minute — no kit required. And if it&rsquo;s not quite right, we swap it free.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="avs-methods">
        <div class="avs-method">
          <span class="avs-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.4"></circle></svg></span>
          <div>
            <h3>Measure a ring you own</h3>
            <p>Take a ring that already fits that finger, measure its <strong>inner diameter</strong> in mm, and match it to the chart below.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="avs-method">
          <span class="avs-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 7h16v10H4z"></path><path d="M8 7v3M12 7v4M16 7v3"></path></svg></span>
          <div>
            <h3>Wrap a strip of paper</h3>
            <p>Wrap paper or string around your finger, mark the overlap, then measure the length in mm — that&rsquo;s your <strong>circumference</strong>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <details class="avs-chart">
        <summary>
          <span>View size chart (US)</span>
          <svg class="avs-chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
        </summary>
        <div class="avs-tablewrap">
          <table class="avs-table">
            <thead><tr><th>US size</th><th>Inner &oslash; (mm)</th><th>Circumference (mm)</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>6</td><td>16.5</td><td>51.9</td></tr>
              <tr><td>7</td><td>17.3</td><td>54.4</td></tr>
              <tr><td>8</td><td>18.1</td><td>57.0</td></tr>
              <tr><td>9</td><td>19.0</td><td>59.5</td></tr>
              <tr><td>10</td><td>19.8</td><td>62.1</td></tr>
              <tr><td>11</td><td>20.6</td><td>64.6</td></tr>
              <tr><td>12</td><td>21.4</td><td>67.2</td></tr>
              <tr><td>13</td><td>22.2</td><td>69.7</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="avs-tip">Measure at the end of the day, when fingers are warmest. Between two sizes? <strong>Size up</strong> — a ring should slide over the knuckle with a little resistance.</p>
      </details>

      <div class="avs-guarantee">
        <span class="avs-gic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.4 8.7 8 11 4.6-2.3 8-6 8-11V5z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></span>
        <p><strong>Free size exchange.</strong> If it doesn&rsquo;t fit, we&rsquo;ll send the right size — on us. No return needed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .avs{background:var(--vg-paper,#fff);padding:56px 20px 8px;font-family:var(--aurora-font,'Inter',sans-serif);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}
  .avs-inner{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;}
  .avs-card{border:1px solid var(--vg-line,#e6e8e3);border-radius:22px;padding:36px 40px;background:var(--vg-paper,#fff);}
  .avs-head{margin-bottom:26px;}
  .avs-eyebrow{display:inline-block;font-family:var(--aurora-mono,monospace);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0d9488;margin-bottom:12px;}
  .avs-h2{font-family:var(--aurora-serif,'Instrument Serif',serif);font-weight:400;color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);font-size:clamp(26px,3.2vw,36px);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 10px;}
  .avs-h2 em{font-style:italic;}
  .avs-sub{color:var(--vg-ink-soft,#5b6066);margin:0;font-size:15.5px;line-height:1.55;max-width:560px;}
  .avs-methods{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-bottom:24px;}
  .avs-method{display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--vg-paper-2,#f5f6f3);border:1px solid var(--vg-line,#e6e8e3);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;}
  .avs-ic{flex-shrink:0;width:40px;height:40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(13,148,136,.08);color:#0d9488;}
  .avs-method h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);margin:2px 0 5px;}
  .avs-method p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--vg-ink-soft,#5b6066);margin:0;}
  .avs-method strong{color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);font-weight:600;}
  .avs-chart{border:1px solid var(--vg-line,#e6e8e3);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:22px;}
  .avs-chart summary{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;cursor:pointer;padding:15px 20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);list-style:none;user-select:none;}
  .avs-chart summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none;}
  .avs-chev{color:var(--vg-ink-soft,#5b6066);transition:transform .25s ease;}
  .avs-chart[open] .avs-chev{transform:rotate(180deg);}
  .avs-tablewrap{overflow-x:auto;padding:0 20px;}
  .avs-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px;min-width:340px;}
  .avs-table th,.avs-table td{padding:9px 10px;text-align:left;border-top:1px solid var(--vg-line,#e6e8e3);}
  .avs-table th{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.03em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--vg-ink-soft,#5b6066);font-weight:600;}
  .avs-table td{color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);}
  .avs-table tbody tr:hover{background:var(--vg-paper-2,#f5f6f3);}
  .avs-tip{margin:14px 20px 18px;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--vg-ink-soft,#5b6066);}
  .avs-tip strong{color:#0d9488;}
  .avs-guarantee{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:rgba(13,148,136,.06);border:1px solid rgba(13,148,136,.18);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px;}
  .avs-gic{flex-shrink:0;width:36px;height:36px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:10px;background:#0d9488;color:#fff;}
  .avs-guarantee p{margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--vg-ink,#15171a);}
  .avs-guarantee strong{font-weight:600;}
  @media(max-width:640px){
    .avs{padding:40px 16px 4px;}
    .avs-card{padding:26px 20px;}
    .avs-methods{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  }
</style>
